{"tid":1490021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先多手上左香港警察個webpage睇左一下","createTime":"2019-08-20T04:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T07:10:40.000Z","uid":243255,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"801dfd44b342eec93f44dd536386547dd2f658a1","tid":1490021,"uid":243255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:08:18.000Z","msg":"警隊抱負、目標及價值觀<br />\n抱負<br />\n<br />\n使香港繼續是世界上其中一個最安全及穩定的社會<br />\n<br />\n目標<br />\n<br />\n為確保社會安穩，香港警隊務必：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">維護法紀<br />\n維持治安<br />\n防止及偵破罪案<br />\n保障市民生命財產</span></strong><br />\n與市民大眾及其他機構維持緊密合作和聯繫<br />\n凡事悉力以赴，力求做得最好<br />\n維持市民對警隊的信心<br />\n價值觀<br />\n<br />\n正直及誠實的品格<br />\n尊重市民及警隊成員的個人權利<br />\n以公正、無私和體諒的態度去處事和對人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">承擔責任及接受問責</span></strong><br />\n專業精神<br />\n致力提供優質服務達至精益求精<br />\n盡量配合環境的轉變<br />\n對內、對外均維持有效的溝通<br />\n<br />\n睇完真係得啖笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5e530ac63074db3ee1aec7cfcad378f0914620","tid":1490021,"uid":34154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>制裁黑警<br />\n審判酷刑罪行<br />\nSanction the Popo<br />\nSend them to Den Haag</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e0c5c277cb04c2fdf4cbd9254d11bffcaa2a6b20","tid":1490021,"uid":209865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"中共做法<br />\n冇既野就寫係頭頂"},{"pid":"a6d633b2d211354ed128bf27ec5170780d02b269","tid":1490021,"uid":243255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"廢老們, 繼續支持克警啦<br />\n<br />\n反正你班人都50up<br />\n<br />\n到時比克警搞 唔好怪人"},{"pid":"7da3005bfa1b82495b18d958e5f3d476e14092b1","tid":1490021,"uid":243255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"睇完內文<br />\n<br />\n其實班狗有D咩係做得到? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c